<div class="allianceSection">
	 <h4 class="header">Characteristic Species</h4>
	<div class="text"> <i>Carex</i> <i>congdonii</i> is characteristically present in the herbaceous layer with <i>Arnica</i> <i>amplexicaulis</i>. Emergent shrubs may be present at low cover, including <i>Sambucus</i> <i>racemosa</i>. </div>
</div>

		
	
<div class="allianceSection">
	 <h4 class="header">Vegetation Layers</h4>
	<div class="text">  Herbs < 90 cm; cover is open. </div>
</div>

		
	
<div class="allianceSection">
	 <h4 class="header">Habitats</h4>
	<div class="text"> Talus and outcrops. Soils are rocky or sandy.  </div>
</div>

		
